{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2bce0418c9","title":"北京矿院党委会员优待条例","origin":"《北京市高等学校大字报选辑》，中央党校社会科学资料室，1957年5月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5bc1a0a83f","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"2bce0418c9"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"3be479694e","name":"卡秋莎"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b053cd5b06","type":"title","text":"北京矿院党委会员优待条例","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bce0418c9"},{"id":"0dd53c2c80","type":"authors","text":"卡秋莎","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bce0418c9"},{"id":"c35bb86f42","type":"paragraph","text":"一、条例宗旨：本条例以树墙掘沟为目的。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bce0418c9"},{"id":"fd7edbe868","type":"paragraph","text":"二、原则：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bce0418c9"},{"id":"422f403597","type":"paragraph","text":"1.本条例以“党员是自己人，群众是外人”为出发点；","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bce0418c9"},{"id":"0b952324e5","type":"paragraph","text":"2.本条例以党员都是100％进步分子，群众都是100％落后分子为出发点。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bce0418c9"},{"id":"43d73551cb","type":"paragraph","text":"三、条例：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bce0418c9"},{"id":"41ab370e26","type":"paragraph","text":"1.提拔升级快者应为党员；","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bce0418c9"},{"id":"12b7895683","type":"paragraph","text":"2.加薪多者应为党员；","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bce0418c9"},{"id":"2cb9a430c2","type":"paragraph","text":"3.出国留学者应为党员；","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bce0418c9"},{"id":"4a747e484b","type":"paragraph","text":"4.出外进修者应为党员；","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bce0418c9"},{"id":"14bc015657","type":"paragraph","text":"5.学习两分可以毕业者应为党员；","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bce0418c9"},{"id":"ea706a178c","type":"paragraph","text":"6.学习很差可以调出作科长、主任者应为党员；","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bce0418c9"},{"id":"1024349639","type":"paragraph","text":"7.生活宽裕可以领取大量补助者应为党员；","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bce0418c9"},{"id":"4fdd150bb3","type":"paragraph","text":"8.虽无需要但可占据大量住房者应为党员；","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bce0418c9"},{"id":"0aabf8f8d4","type":"paragraph","text":"9.运用职权安插亲友者应为党员；","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bce0418c9"},{"id":"9378ebfd22","type":"paragraph","text":"10.不会跳舞可以领取北京饭店高级舞票者应为党员；","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bce0418c9"},{"id":"cf5011ff8d","type":"paragraph","text":"11.半年不工作照领工资者应为党员；","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bce0418c9"},{"id":"38aeb66c02","type":"paragraph","text":"12.不是高级知识分子可以照顾高级知识分子优待证者应为党员；","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bce0418c9"},{"id":"d23c8eda26","type":"paragraph","text":"13.爱人优先调来者应为党员；","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bce0418c9"},{"id":"9bd4bf16c8","type":"paragraph","text":"14.两年不交工会会费，非但可以不加任何处分而且可以领取工会大量补助者应为党员；","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bce0418c9"},{"id":"b97313f19f","type":"paragraph","text":"15.长期住疗养院但仍照样升级加薪者应为党员；","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bce0418c9"},{"id":"4a1e18cecf","type":"paragraph","text":"16.违法乱纪，强奸妇女，不依法惩办者应为党员。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bce0418c9"},{"id":"643e469fb7","type":"paragraph","text":"四、附则：","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bce0418c9"},{"id":"19e139f902","type":"paragraph","text":"本条例项目繁多难以一一列举，得因时间地点条件之不同，灵活掌握。以符合“享乐在前，吃苦在后”的精神。","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bce0418c9"}],"page":{"id":"0e1c28029c","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bce0418c9","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}